criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. acute leukemia patient according to 2008 WHO criteria, including acute lymphoblastic leukemia, acute myloied leukemia with intermediate risk and poor risk;
2. Aged more than 14 years old and less than 60 years old;
3. Physical score 0~2（WHO);
4. Sign the informed consent document.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. diagnosis as acute myloied leukemia with better risk;
2. contraindication of hematopoietic stem cell transplantation, e.g. uncontrolled active infection and severe cardiac, hepatic, renal and pulmonary disease;
3. Pregnant;
4. Mental disorder;
5. Physical score>3（WHO);
6. Cann't sign the informed consent document.
